story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0100_: Hahaha! You’re quite a good detective!
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0200_:
I didn’t expect you to so quickly uncover a disguise
I worked on!
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0300_:
(Well... The one who saw through the disguise
was Mimi, but...)
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0500_:
Prepare yourself, Team Rocket! We’re taking every
last one of you into custody!
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0800_:
Whoa! I guess he does have the skills to back up
his big claims!
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_0900_:
Hate to break it to ya, but this is as far as
you go.
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_1000_:
*chuckle* Oh, you thought you could just power
through us?
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_1100_:
Sorry to cut your celebration short, but we’ll finish
you off now.
story_teamflare_02_08000/2401_1001_1200_:
Uh-oh... The other executives came to back
them up!
